page.title: 06HOUSING IN LAMLASH SOUTH.
page.content: Following the road South you become aware of the change in age of the buildings here being considerably younger than the previous ones.The end of the housing areas starts at Cordon just off the main road,almost being a small settlement on its own consisting of small cottages.While further on the last two housing areas begin called Murray Estate and Murray Cresent on the either side of the road.Murray Estate runs along the road with all its houses facing the road, while Murray Cresent on the other hand is a very modern housing estate consisting of small bungaloes.
